  Ms MURPHY (

Dunkley
) (
10:30
):  The ABC and the SBS are our treasured and trusted independent broadcasters. They are not only a source of reliable news; the ABC, in particular, provides Australian voices, Australian faces and Australian stories to us and to our region, and for many locals in Dunkley the SBS is a portal to the rest of the world. That's why it is so important to provide certainty for these national broadcasters with five-year funding terms, which is exactly what an Albanese Labor government would provide, to improve their capacity to innovate and plan within the diverse ecosystems they support in education, screen production and international broadcasting.
